                     <a id="a000102"></a>
                     <div class="content" id="entry-102">
                        <h3 class="content">pimp my ride: combining car mods with d&d</h3>
                        <div class="content">
                           <div class="content">
                              <p><img src="http://drzaius.ics.uci.edu/mt3.14/johannab/archives/diemod.jpg" width="160" height="171"></p>

<p>it is so cool to take you love of dungeons & dragons and <a href="http://forums.privateerpress.com/index.php?showtopic=37279">merge it with your stick shift</a>.  it really is. </p>

<p>[thanks <a href="http://www.gizmodo.com/gadgets/gadgets/vehicles/d20-stick-shift-033892.php">gizmodo</a>]</p>
                              
                              <p class="posted">
